"주문날짜 초기값 세팅
IF S_DDATE[] IS INITIAL.
    CONCATENATE SY-DATUM(4) '01' '01' INTO S_DDATE-LOW.
    S_DDATE-HIGH = SY-DATUM(6) && '01'. "&&로도 표현 가능 (=CONCATENATE)
    S_DDATE-SIGN = 'I'.
    S_DDATE-OPTION = 'BT'.

    CALL FUNCTION 'LAST_DAY_OF_MONTHS'
        EXPORTING
        DAY_IN            = S_DDATE-HIGH
        IMPORTING
        LAST_DAY_OF_MONTH = S_DDATE-HIGH.

    APPEND S_DDATE.
ENDIF.